OL,3,CTechnology 'being weaponised' against
OL,4,Cschools and teachers ` union leader
OL,6,FSmartphones and social media are
OL,7,Fincreasingly "being weaponised"
OL,8,Fagainst schools and teachers, a
OL,9,Fheadteachers' union leader will say.
OL,11,FManny Botwe, president of the
OL,12,FAssociation of School and College
OL,13,FLeaders (ASCL), will say technology
OL,14,Fhas a "darker side" and leaves a
OL,15,F"trail of harm".
OL,17,FIn a speech at the union's annual
OL,18,Fconference on Friday, Mr Botwe will
OL,19,Fwarn that "disgruntled parents" are
OL,20,Fusing online sites to target school
OL,21,Fstaff.
