OL,6,FMr Botwe will call for an end to the
OL,7,F"chaos" caused by social media and he
OL,8,Fwill say it is time to bring social
OL,9,Fmedia platforms to "heel".
OL,11,FHis comments come as a survey for ASCL
OL,12,Ffound that 71% of teachers said pupils
OL,13,Fwere using social media below the
OL,14,Fminimum age requirement.
OL,16,FThe poll by the Teacher Tapp app asked
OL,17,F6,409 teachers and leaders in schools
OL,18,Fin England in February what social
OL,19,Fmedia-related issues they had noticed
OL,20,Fsince September.
