OL,6,FThe president of the ASCL will call
OL,7,Fthe survey findings "deeply troubling"
OL,8,Fon Friday.
OL,10,FAddressing around 1,000 school and
OL,11,Fcollege leaders at the Arena and
OL,12,FConvention Centre (ACC) in Liverpool,
OL,13,FMr Botwe will say young people's
OL,14,Fworlds are shaped by smartphones,
OL,15,Fsocial media, memes and influencers.
OL,17,FMr Botwe is expected to warn: "It
OL,18,Fleaves a trail of harm ` safeguarding
OL,19,Fconcerns, fractured friendships,
OL,20,Fbullying, anxiety and the spread of
OL,21,Fextremist ideologies.
