OL,3,CTechnology 'being weaponised' against
OL,4,Cschools and teachers ` union leader
OL,6,F"And increasingly, it is being
OL,7,Fweaponised against schools and
OL,8,Fteachers, with disgruntled parents
OL,9,Fusing it as a platform to target
OL,10,Fstaff."
OL,12,FMr Botwe, head of Tytherington School
OL,13,Fin Macclesfield, Cheshire, will add:
OL,14,F"For too long, tech billionaires have
OL,15,Fbeen given immense power without
OL,16,Faccountability.
OL,18,F"They hide behind the defence that
OL,19,Fthey are champions of free speech
OL,20,Fwhile profiting from platforms that
OL,21,Fallow harm to fester.
