OL,6,F"But enough is enough. It is time to
OL,7,Fbring these platforms to heel and
OL,8,Fforce them to police their own spaces.
OL,10,F"While we welcome the Online Safety
OL,11,FAct we have yet to see its protections
OL,12,Fcome into force and or how effective
OL,13,Fthey prove in practice."
OL,15,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,16,Fand Ofsted's chief inspector Sir
OL,17,FMartyn Oliver are also due to address
OL,18,Fschool and college leaders at ASCL's
OL,19,Fannual conference in Liverpool on
OL,20,FFriday.
