OL,6,FMr Botwe will criticise the
OL,7,FGovernment's proposed Children's
OL,8,FWellbeing and Schools Bill for being
OL,9,F"fragmented" and he will describe it a
OL,10,F"smorgasbord of policies" which lacks
OL,11,Fa clear, overarching vision.
OL,13,FOn the Government's plans for free
OL,14,Fbreakfast clubs in primary schools, he
OL,15,Fwill say that a basic daily funding
OL,16,Frate of 60p per pupil is "absurd".
